{"tid":1443211,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"落北角的沙盤推演","createTime":"2019-08-11T07:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T08:00:25.000Z","uid":270820,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bf9c9314f70df69b7afdd19456e2f20d177038ca","tid":1443211,"uid":270820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:10:56.000Z","msg":"依家全北角係防暴+黑衫，最可能發生係<br />\n1. 我地一落場被一字排開抄牌(抄左牌機乎之後無得落場)<br />\n2. 白衫隔住差佬身後叫囂/抽水，無後果<br />\n3. 我地反擊，街坊，白衫，黑警輪流岀手，畫面傳反上去俾人做文章<br />\n4. 我地打贏，前中後排都有人被捕<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">5. 白衫頭破血流畫面傳上去，陸續到汕頭幫，潮洲幫，仲要免費自發落黎，沒完沒了，咁運動呢？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n分析：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 我地一向有彈岀彈入共識<br />\n2. 福建幫響整場運動入面根本係唔關事食花生</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔落北角會發生咩事呢？<br />\n<br />\n1. 福建幫打咭影相，但市面風平浪靜<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以何律師性格一定走數，因為都無交打點會俾錢</span></span></strong><br />\n3. 福建幫收唔倒錢，以後無下次，採佢有味<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4. 文宣進場，風向改變，福建幫由保家衛族變成生意剋星，私人團購<br />\n5. 將XX幫=鄉黑，黑警，同街坊，商人切割</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家諗一諗，如果情況類同，各區可以參考一下"},{"pid":"0d71bb3957353373e88dda5f09287b9d70c4fbc4","tid":1443211,"uid":270820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:12:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6843b6103635ed1ba49f8110629538a3c3d6c46c","tid":1443211,"uid":270820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:13:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2991eff0e20677e5987ff951d48b2056c332ec18","tid":1443211,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:14:23.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"7bf8c2b3fefa320d347fce8fa64a98c361432084","tid":1443211,"uid":270820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:16:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ce48bc4913f09488f0747e3222feeffabe48ac7","tid":1443211,"uid